{{Quote|You'd be surprised how interesting underwater mining is to watch. Actually, at full capacity the casino could probably pay the overhead for the whole operation all by itself.|Lando Calrissian|<ref name="Specter of the Past">''[[Specter of the Past]]''</ref>}}
'''''Deep Pockets''''' was an underwater mining complex on [[Varn]] owned by [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] in [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]]. Following the start of the venture, Calrissian added on a casino and observation gallery to the facility, with financing from [[Tendra Risant Calrissian|Tendra Risant's]] family, despite their skepticism. At full capacity, the casino's total revenue could pay for the entire operation, and many customers were actually delighted to pay money to observe Lando's miners at work. However, [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] raids on Varn wore into the operation.

It contained the [[Tralus Room]] and was commanded by [[Donnerwin]].

